features: Power bank high speed 22.5W combines the most advanced PD 30W fast charging technologies can charge your iPhone incredibly fast from 0 to 60% in just 30 minutes, nearly 2X faster than other traditional chargers.

Portable charger is designed with 4 outputs: 1 USB-A port(SCP22.5W), 1 Type-C port (PD30W), 1 IOS charging cable and 1 Type-C charging cable (SCP22.5W). Portable charger is also equipped with 2 inputs: USB-A port and Type-C port.

Portable charger power bank is different from most chargers featuring a Type-C input only, power bank has a Type-C In & Out port to perfect for your new iPhone, iPad and all upcoming Type-C devices.（Attention: Type-C cable cannot charge iPhone15 series, but Type-C port can)

Portable charger has 16000mAh capacity, battery pack charger portable allows you to charge your devices multiple times. Let you get rid of the anxiety of mobile device power anytime and everywhere. Ensures you have enough power to enjoy your trip.

Portable charger power bank equipped with high quality smart chip to extend the life of portable charger and help protect your devices from over-temperature, overcharge, short circuit. Multi-protection security system to provide complete protection for you and your devices.
